 * Find a path from (startX, startY) to (goalX, goalY) on a walkable grid.
 * @param {boolean[][]} walkable  - walkable[row][col]
 * @param {number} cols
 * @param {number} rows
 * @returns {Array<{tx,ty}>|null}  - list of steps NOT including start; null if no path
